{"tid":1332323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣求救] 3張太空卡個whatsapp用都未用過就比人ban左","createTime":"2019-07-19T09:15:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T10:30:15.000Z","uid":156666,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"243eb5b0c17aa1b8c2c97d9931f7ed4a1cf95aef","tid":1332323,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:15:24.000Z","msg":"我一入去佢就ban左我<br />\n佢係咪check住我部「機」?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M2a9xSR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM2a9xSR.jpg&h=9d4a728c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n深水埗160蚊買左8張黎做文宣 <br />\n而家得番一張冇比人封<br />\n===========================<br />\n文宣內容: (請逐個人send唔好send group:逐個人send啲人先會睇) <br />\n(針對廢老既行動我已經完成左,而家打算針對番淺黃諗緊出唔出既人)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EOhcvE4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEOhcvE4.jpg&h=83e46d05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「不自由，毋寧死！」<br />\n香港人已經取代維吾爾族，成為中共既頭號眼中釘 <br />\n運動一旦開始冷卻，共產黨必然會以最快速度清洗香港人<br />\n香港人善忘，但係共產黨絕對不善忘，仲好記仇<br />\n今次運動只許成功，絕對不許失敗，否則香港人會一個一個被送入集中營。而且無人會黎救<br />\n監控燈柱，信用系統，不需多講，大家都明，係對香港完全壓制清洗既前期功夫。<br />\n香港人，要有絕對既覺悟，明白失敗既結果，會比死更慘。<br />\n妻離子散，失去自由。<br />\n係監禁中痛苦為共產黨做奴隸，直至死亡。<br />\n大家7.21金鐘見。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OmNoCk6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOmNoCk6.jpg&h=f92bb2cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ac517188cea22635b6b14cc722089ec3bd75634","tid":1332323,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:15:55.000Z","msg":"有4張係文宣成功之後先被封"},{"pid":"9be60f3e05f067ea0fc4fefc10c1769f6ccfd73b","tid":1332323,"uid":1159,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:16:51.000Z","msg":"有機會bam埋IMEI"},{"pid":"ce2ed1077f12ddf40240ee6915869ddc1a96f5b6","tid":1332323,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:17:16.000Z","msg":"btw 有張卡仲有上一手既資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係2017年DSE某元朗中